          <title>
            <string language="en">Paint x 3: Robert Bechtle</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Malen Sie x 3: Robert Bechtle</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Peignez x 3 : Robert Bechtle</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Pinte x 3: Robert Bechtle</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Vernici la x 3: Robert Bechtle</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Χρώμα Χ 3: Θ*Ροψερτ Bechtle</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Pinte x 3: Roberto Bechtle</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">American Photorealist painter Robert Bechtle prepares for a retrospective exhibit of his work at the San Francisco Museum of Modern Art. This Educator Guide address the history and evolution of photorealism in painting.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Arts</string>
          </keyword>
          <coverage>
            <string language="en">North America</string>
          </coverage>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Amerikanischer Photorealist Maler Robert Bechtle 
bereitet sich für eine zurückblickende Ausstellung seiner Arbeit am 
San Francisco Museum der modernen kunst vor. Diese 
Erzieher-Anleitungadresse die Geschichte und die Entwicklung von 
photorealism im Anstrich.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Le peintre américain Robert Bechtle de 
Photorealist se prépare à un objet exposé rétrospectif de son 
travail au musée de San Francisco de l'art moderne. Cette 
adresse de guide d'éducateur l'histoire et l'évolution du 
photorealism dans la peinture.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">O pintor americano Robert Bechtle de Photorealist 
prepara-se para uma exibição retrospective de seu trabalho no museu 
do San Francisco da arte moderna. Este endereço da guia do 
educador o history e a evolução do photorealism na pintura.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Il pittore americano Robert Bechtle di 
Photorealist si prepara per un'esposizione retrospettiva del suo 
lavoro al museo de San Francisco dell'arte moderna. Questo 
indirizzo della guida dell'educatore la storia e lo sviluppo del 
photorealism nella pittura.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ο αμερικανικός Photorealist ζωγράφος Robert 
Bechtle προετοιμάζεται για ένα αναδρομικό έκθεμα της εργασίας 
του στο μουσείο του Σαν Φρανσίσκο της μοντέρνας τέχνης. 
Αυτός ο οδηγός εκπαιδευτικών εξετάζει την ιστορία και την 
εξέλιξη του photorealism στη ζωγραφική.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El pintor americano Roberto Bechtle de 
Photorealist se prepara para un objeto expuesto retrospectivo de su 
trabajo en el museo de San Francisco del arte moderno. Este 
direccionamiento de la guía del educador la historia y la evolución 
del photorealism en la pintura.</string>
          </description>
